Text:
Really cool list,though some of them seems annoying as the first time you heard them in the eighties.

A little request though,in all honor;
Could you get Rock 'n' Roll Hits* by Various Artists for me,there's a whole bunch of people interested in it.
I could buy it and upload it,but then i'd probably be too late.
